rameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/442410187\"></iframe></div></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li></ul>\n","\n<ul class=\"maintree ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-isolate-scope ui-sortable ng-not-empty\"><li id=\"1nYBw\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list header, listed   ui-resizable\"><div class=\"asset-header ng-binding\"></div><div class=\"head editable ng-pristine ng-valid ng-binding ng-scope ng-not-empty None ng-touched background\" ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\" spellcheck=\"false\"><h5 class=\"background\">Types of Optimism<br></h5></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li><li id=\"Q4v9c\" data-space=\"video\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list listed selected-class video-box   border active,\"><div class=\"asset-header ng-binding\"></div><div class=\"video-edit editable ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-scope None ng-not-empty\"><div class=\"video-content active\"><p>Select your Video URL in the Edit Panel</p><span class=\"icon-video\"></span></div><div class=\"js-video [vimeo, widescreen] active\"><iframe frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/442410187\"></iframe></div></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li></ul>\n","\n<ul class=\"maintree ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-isolate-scope ui-sortable ng-not-empty\"><li id=\"my9L1\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list header, listed   ui-resizable\"><div class=\"asset-header ng-binding\"></div><div class=\"head editable ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-binding ng-scope ng-not-empty None\" ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\"><h5>Lesson Summary</h5></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li><li id=\"XQnkt\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list list-item, listed selected-class   border ui-resizable\"><div class=\"asset-header ng-binding\"></div><div ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\" class=\"list-item editable ng-pristine ng-valid ng-binding ng-scope ng-not-empty None ng-touched\" spellcheck=\"false\"><ul class=\"\"><li class=\"\">Affect is the broad range of feelings that people experience. It can be in the form of emotions or moods. The functions of emotion are rationality and evolutionary psychology.</li><li class=\"\">Emotions can be generated from the days of the week, the weather, stress, social activities, sleep, or the lack of sleep.&nbsp; Emotions and moods can be applied on motivating workers, leadership, negotiation, excellent customer service delivery.</li><li class=\"\">Frustration is the blocking or slowing down of a goal-directed objective. It is usually caused by privation, deprivation, and conflict.</li><li class=\"\">The six types of personality are conventional, realistic, investigative, artistic, social, and enterprise.</li><li class=\"\">Manager cans use humor to lighten moods, give a small token of appreciation, lead by example, and hire more positive people.</li><li class=\"\">Optimism is the belief that good will ultimately prevail in the world. It is a state of being positive. Optimism is an individual difference variable that reflects the extent to which people hold generalized favorable expectancies about their future.</li><li class=\"\">The types of optimism are personal optimism and self-efficacy optimism.</li><li class=\"\">Optimism is different from hope and realism.</li><li class=\"\">Theories of optimism are the theory of explanatory style and the theory of dispositional optimism.&nbsp;</li></ul></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li></ul>\n","\n<ul class=\"maintree ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-isolate-scope ui-sortable ng-not-empty\"><li id=\"TDKhr\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list header, listed   ui-resizable\"><div class=\"asset-header ng-binding\"></div><div class=\"head editable ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-binding ng-scope ng-not-empty None\" ng-pas