ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\" spellcheck=\"false\"><h5 class=\"background\">Antecedents of Adaptive Performance<br></h5></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li><li id=\"6oPbU\" data-space=\"video\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list listed selected-class video-box   border active,\"><div class=\"asset-header ng-binding\"></div><div class=\"video-edit editable ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-scope None ng-not-empty\"><div class=\"video-content active\"><p>Select your Video URL in the Edit Panel</p><span class=\"icon-video\"></span></div><div class=\"js-video [vimeo, widescreen] active\"><iframe frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/442412717\"></iframe></div></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li></ul>\n","\n<ul class=\"maintree ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-isolate-scope ui-sortable ng-not-empty\"><li id=\"aT5lE\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list header, listed   ui-resizable\"><div class=\"asset-header ng-binding\"></div><div class=\"head editable ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-valid ng-binding ng-scope ng-not-empty None\" ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\"><h5>Lesson Summary</h5></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li><li id=\"Qcrvb\" data-space=\"\" full-editor=\"\" class=\"component list list-item, listed selected-class   ui-resizable border\"><div class=\"asset-header ng-binding\"></div><div ng-paste=\"removeFormat($event, item.title)\" class=\"list-item editable ng-pristine ng-valid ng-binding ng-scope ng-not-empty None ng-touched\" spellcheck=\"false\"><ul class=\"\"><li class=\"\"><div>Career engagement is defined as the emotional and cognitive connection to one's career. The degree to which an individual is proactively unveiling different career behavior.&nbsp;</div></li><li class=\"\"><div>An individual's career decision often has an impact on his or her career success.&nbsp;</div></li><li class=\"\"><div>Human capital theory suggests that obtaining a fit between your human capital investment and job requirement generates rewards in terms of higher pay which leads to engagement.</div></li><li class=\"\"><div>There are three wheels of career engagement that helps an individual to evaluate his or her career engagement.&nbsp;</div></li><li class=\"\"><div>Today, organizations are characterized by a constantly changing and dynamic environment. This, therefore, implies that the need for adaptive workers in the organization is constantly increasing.</div></li><li class=\"\"><div>According to the Centre for Creative Leadership, adaptability can be achieved in three steps. One is through ideas, change, and facts.<br></div></li><li class=\"\"><div>There are three types of flexibility, and they are Cognitive, Emotional, and Dispositional flexibility.</div></li><li class=\"\"><div>Adaptability is the key function of flexibility. It leads to managerial effectiveness.<br></div></li></ul></div><div class=\"caption ng-binding\"></div></li></ul>\n"]}